comment:
* Additional options when requesting Face authentication or detection.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: mUserId
variables.comment: The user id for this operation.

variables.name: mSensorId
variables.comment: The sensor id for this operation.

variables.name: mDisplayState
variables.comment: The current doze state of the device.

variables.name: mAuthenticateReason
variables.comment:
* The reason for this operation when requested by the system (sysui),
     * otherwise AUTHENTICATE_REASON_UNKNOWN.
     *
     * See frameworks/base/packages/SystemUI/src/com/android/keyguard/FaceAuthReason.kt
     * for more details about each reason.

variables.name: mWakeReason
variables.comment: A reason if this request was triggered due to a power event or WAKE_REASON_UNKNOWN.

variables.name: mOpPackageName
variables.comment:
* The package name for that operation that should be used for
     * {@link android.app.AppOpsManager} verification.
     *
     * This option may be overridden by the FingerprintManager using the caller's context.

variables.name: mAttributionTag
variables.comment:
* The attribution tag, if any.
     *
     * This option may be overridden by the FingerprintManager using the caller's context.
